        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            <a href="/en/dep/ud/campaign/delimitation.html?id=614002" class="ISI_IGNORE">
                <img src="/upload/UD/Ingressbilder/Delelinjen_undert_ingress.jpg" alt="Photo: M.Kopstad, MFA, Oslo" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/ud/campaign/delimitation.html?id=614002" title="">
                        The treaty on maritime delimitation between Norway and Russia
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Campaign, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 15.09.2010]</p>
                <p>On 15 September 2010, Norway and Russia signed the Treaty concerning Maritime Delimitation and Cooperation in the Barents Sea and the Arctic Ocean. It was signed in Murmansk by Foreign Ministers Jonas Gahr Støre and Sergei Lavrov in the presence of Prime Minister Jens Stoltenberg and President Dmitry Medvedev.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                <span id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_SubjectManager_wp1911044452_wp2011366416_lstSearchResult_lstUniversal_ctl05_Label1"></span>                 
