        </div> 
    
        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            <a href="/en/dep/smk/press-center/Press-releases/2010/Treaty-between-Norway-and-Russia-to-be-signed.html?id=613684" class="ISI_IGNORE">
                <img src="/upload/SMK/Nyhetsbilder/2010/Avtale_Norge_Russland_100x75.jpg" alt="" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/smk/press-center/Press-releases/2010/Treaty-between-Norway-and-Russia-to-be-signed.html?id=613684" title="">
                        Treaty between Norway and Russia to be signed
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, The Office of the Prime Minister, 06.09.2010]</p>
                <p>Norway and Russia will sign the Treaty concerning Maritime Delimitation and Cooperation in the Barents Sea and the Arctic Ocean in Murmansk on 15 September. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                <span id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_SubjectManager_wp1911044452_wp2011366416_lstSearchResult_lstUniversal_ctl06_Label1"></span>                 
