        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/ud/aktuelt/taler_artikler/taler_og_artikler_av_ovrig_politisk_lede/taler_lahnstein/2010/cbss_mariehamn.html?id=613360" title="">
                        Cooperation in the Baltic Sea Region from the CBSS perspective
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">The 19th Baltic Sea Parliamentary Conference, Mariehamn 30 August 2010</h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Speech/article, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 30.08.2010]</p>
                <p>On behalf of the Norwegian chairmanship of the Council of the Baltic Sea States State Secretary Erik Lahnstein gave this address about Norwegian priorities for the chairmanship at the Baltic Sea parliamentarians conference, Mariehamn, Åland, 30 August.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                <span id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_SubjectManager_wp1911044452_wp2011366416_lstSearchResult_lstUniversal_ctl07_Label1"></span>                 
