                <img src="/upload/UD/Ingressbilder/jgs_foredrag_ingress.jpg" alt="Støre in Beijing 30 August 2010. Photo: B.Svenungsen, MFA, Oslo" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/ud/aktuelt/taler_artikler/utenriksministeren/2010/ciis_beijing.html?id=613162" title="">
                        The Arctic – Norwegian Policy and International Cooperation
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Speech/article, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 30.08.2010]</p>
                <p>- Developments in the Arctic have global effects. Global actors have legitimate interests in the region and can make a valuable contribution. That is why we are here today, Minister Støre said in his speech about the Arctic and the High North in Beijing 30 August.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                <span id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_SubjectManager_wp1911044452_wp2011366416_lstSearchResult_lstUniversal_ctl08_Label1"></span>                 
